1](data:image/svg+xml;charset=utf8,%3Csvg%20xmlns%3D%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.w3.org%2F2000%2Fsvg%22%20xmlns%3Awrs%3D%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.wiris.com%2Fxml%2Fcvs-extension%22%20height%3D%2219%22%20width%3D%2233%22%20wrs%3Abaseline%3D%2215%22%3E%3C%21--MathML%3A%20%3Cmath%20xmlns%3D%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.w3.org%2F1998%2FMath%2FMathML%22%20style%3D%22font-family%3A%27Times%20New%20Roman%27%22%3E%3Cmi%3Ek%3C%2Fmi%3E%3Cmo%3E%26%23x2265%3B%3C%2Fmo%3E%3Cmn%3E1%3C%2Fmn%3E%3C%2Fmath%3E--%3E%3Cdefs%3E%3Cstyle%20type%3D%22text%2Fcss%22%3E%40font-face%7Bfont-family%3A%27math1070c425fd005e11aec1a90706d%27%3Bsrc%3Aurl%28data%3Afont%2Ftruetype%3Bcharset%3Dutf-8%3Bbase64%%2F%2FwAAImX%2F%2F92cAAEAAAAAAAABVAMsAIABAABWACoCWAIeAQ4BLAIsAFoBgAKAAKAA1ACAAAAAAAAAACsAVQCAAKsA1QEAASsABwAAAAIAVQAAAwADqwADAAcAADMRIRElIREhVQKr%2FasCAP4AA6v8VVUDAAADAID%2FqwKBAqsAAwAHAAsALxgBALEJAD%2BxCAXksQIF9LEBBPSxBgX0sQME5LEFBPSxBAX0sQcBEDyxAAYQPDAxARUBNRE1ARUBNSEVAoD%2BAAIB%2Ff8CAAGrVv8AVgGqVv8AVv5WVVUAAAEAAAABAADVeM5BXw889QADBAD%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F1joTc%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2FWOhNzAAD%2FIASAA6sAAAAKAAIAAQAAAAAAAQAAA%2Bj%2FagAAF3AAAP%%2F%29format%28%27truetype%27%29%3Bfont-weight%3Anormal%3Bfont-style%3Anormal%3B%7D%3C%2Fstyle%3E%3C%2Fdefs%3E%3Ctext%20font-family%3D%22Times%20New%20Roman%22%20font-size%3D%2216%22%20font-style%3D%22italic%22%20text-anchor%3D%22middle%22%20x%3D%224.5%22%20y%3D%2215%22%3Ek%3C%2Ftext%3E%3Ctext%20font-family%3D%22math1070c425fd005e11aec1a90706d%22%20font-size%3D%2214%22%20text-anchor%3D%22middle%22%20x%3D%2216.5%22%20y%3D%2215%22%3E%26%23x2265%3B%3C%2Ftext%3E%3Ctext%20font-family%3D%22Times%20New%20Roman%22%20font-size%3D%2216%22%20text-anchor%3D%22middle%22%20x%3D%2228.5%22%20y%3D%2215%22%3E1%3C%2Ftext%3E%3C%2Fsvg%3E)，容积为![k 乘號 V](data:image/svg+xml;charset=utf8,%3Csvg%20xmlns%3D%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.w3.org%2F2000%2Fsvg%22%20xmlns%3Awrs%3D%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.wiris.com%2Fxml%2Fcvs-extension%22%20height%3D%2219%22%20width%3D%2237%22%20wrs%3Abaseline%3D%2215%22%3E%3C%21--MathML%3A%20%3Cmath%20xmlns%3D%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.w3.org%2F1998%2FMath%2FMathML%22%20style%3D%22font-family%3A%27Times%20New%20Roman%27%22%3E%3Cmi%3Ek%3C%2Fmi%3E%3Cmo%3E%26%23xD7%3B%3C%2Fmo%3E%3Cmi%3EV%3C%2Fmi%3E%3C%2Fmath%3E--%3E%3Cdefs%3E%3Cstyle%20type%3D%22text%2Fcss%22%3E%40font-face%7Bfont-family%3A%27math13b8a614226a953a8cd9526fca6%27%3Bsrc%3Aurl%28data%3Afont%2Ftruetype%3Bcharset%3Dutf-8%3Bbase64%%2F%2FwAAANf%2F%2F%2F8qAAEAAAAAAAABVAMsAIABAABWACoCWAIeAQ4BLAIsAFoBgAKAAKAA1ACAAAAAAAAAACsAVQCAAKsA1QEAASsABwAAAAIAVQAAAwADqwADAAcAADMRIRElIREhVQKr%2FasCAP4AA6v8VVUDAAACAIAAVQLVAoAAAwAHAEYYsAEUALEAABMQsQAJ5LEAARMQsAQ8sQYI9LACPDABsQgBExCxAAP2sAc8sQEF9bAGPLIFBwAQ9LACPLEJA%2BaxBAX1sAM8EzMBIxEzASOAVQIAVVX%2BAFUCgP3VAiv91QAAAQAAAAEAANV4zkFfDzz1AAMEAP%2F%2F%2F%2F%2FWOhNz%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F9Y6E3MAAP8gBIADqwAAAAoAAgABAAAAAAABAAAD6P9qAAAXcAAA%%2BgAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAuQcRAACNhRgAsgAAABUUE7EAAT8%3D%29format%28%27truetype%27%29%3Bfont-weight%3Anormal%3Bfont-style%3Anormal%3B%7D%3C%2Fstyle%3E%3C%2Fdefs%3E%3Ctext%20font-family%3D%22Times%20New%20Roman%22%20font-size%3D%2216%22%20font-style%3D%22italic%22%20text-anchor%3D%22middle%22%20x%3D%224.5%22%20y%3D%2215%22%3Ek%3C%2Ftext%3E%3Ctext%20font-family%3D%22math13b8a614226a953a8cd9526fca6%22%20font-size%3D%2214%22%20text-anchor%3D%22middle%22%20x%3D%2216.5%22%20y%3D%2215%22%3E%26%23xD7%3B%3C%2Ftext%3E%3Ctext%20font-family%3D%22Times%20New%20Roman%22%20font-size%3D%2216%22%20font-style%3D%22italic%22%20text-anchor%3D%22middle%22%20x%3D%2229.5%22%20y%3D%2215%22%3EV%3C%2Ftext%3E%3C%2Fsvg%3E)的背包都存在。

龙神有一些物品要装进背包，第![i](data:image/svg+xml;charset=utf8,%3Csvg%20xmlns%3D%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.w3.org%2F2000%2Fsvg%22%20xmlns%3Awrs%3D%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.wiris.com%2Fxml%2Fcvs-extension%22%20height%3D%2219%22%20width%3D%226%22%20wrs%3Abaseline%3D%2215%22%3E%3C%21--MathML%3A%20%3Cmath%20xmlns%3D%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.w3.org%2F1998%2FMath%2FMathML%22%20style%3D%22font-family%3A%27Times%20New%20Roman%27%22%3E%3Cmi%3Ei%3C%2Fmi%3E%3C%2Fmath%3E--%3E%3Cdefs%3E%3Cstyle%20type%3D%22text%2Fcss%22%2F%3E%3C%2Fdefs%3E%3Ctext%20font-family%3D%22Times%20New%20Roman%22%20font-size%3D%2216%22%20font-style%3D%22italic%22%20text-anchor%3D%22middle%22%20x%3D%222.5%22%20y%3D%2215%22%3Ei%3C%2Ftext%3E%3C%2Fsvg%3E)个物品占据![p 下標 i](data:image/svg+xml;charset=utf8,%3Csvg%20xmlns%3D%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.w3.org%2F2000%2Fsvg%22%20xmlns%3Awrs%3D%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.wiris.com%2Fxml%2Fcvs-extension%22%20height%3D%2226%22%20width%3D%2214%22%20wrs%3Abaseline%3D%2215%22%3E%3C%21--MathML%3A%20%3Cmath%20xmlns%3D%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.w3.org%2F1998%2FMath%2FMathML%22%20style%3D%22font-family%3A%27Times%20New%20Roman%27%22%3E%3Cmsub%3E%3Cmi%3Ep%3C%2Fmi%3E%3Cmi%3Ei%3C%2Fmi%3E%3C%2Fmsub%3E%3C%2Fmath%3E--%3E%3Cdefs%3E%3Cstyle%20type%3D%22text%2Fcss%22%2F%3E%3C%2Fdefs%3E%3Ctext%20font-family%3D%22Times%20New%20Roman%22%20font-size%3D%2216%22%20font-style%3D%22italic%22%20text-anchor%3D%22middle%22%20x%3D%224.5%22%20y%3D%2215%22%3Ep%3C%2Ftext%3E%3Ctext%20font-family%3D%22Times%20New%20Roman%22%20font-size%3D%2212%22%20font-style%3D%22italic%22%20text-anchor%3D%22middle%22%20x%3D%2210.5%22%20y%3D%2222%22%3Ei%3C%2Ftext%3E%3C%2Fsvg%3E)的体积。现在，龙神想选出一些物品，使得存在一个背包可以恰好放下这些物品，并且这个背包放满。

龙神想知道这样的取法有多少个，请你帮他算一算吧？由于取法很多，你只需要输出取法的末七位数即可（即对10000000取模）。

**Input:**

第二行![n](data:image/svg+xml;charset=utf8,%3Csvg%20xmlns%3D%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.w3.org%2F2000%2Fsvg%22%20xmlns%3Awrs%3D%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.wiris.com%2Fxml%2Fcvs-extension%22%20height%3D%2219%22%20width%3D%2210%22%20wrs%3Abaseline%3D%2215%22%3E%3C%21--MathML%3A%20%3Cmath%20xmlns%3D%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.w3.org%2F1998%2FMath%2FMathML%22%20style%3D%22font-family%3A%27Times%20New%20Roman%27%22%3E%3Cmi%3En%3C%2Fmi%3E%3C%2Fmath%3E--%3E%3Cdefs%3E%3Cstyle%20type%3D%22text%2Fcss%22%2F%3E%3C%2Fdefs%3E%3Ctext%20font-family%3D%22Times%20New%20Roman%22%20font-size%3D%2216%22%20font-style%3D%22italic%22%20text-anchor%3D%22middle%22%20x%3D%224.5%22%20y%3D%2215%22%3En%3C%2Ftext%3E%3C%2Fsvg%3E)个数，分别表示每个物品的体积![p 下標 i](data:image/svg+xml;charset=utf8,%3Csvg%20xmlns%3D%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.w3.org%2F2000%2Fsvg%22%20xmlns%3Awrs%3D%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.wiris.com%2Fxml%2Fcvs-extension%22%20height%3D%2226%22%20width%3D%2214%22%20wrs%3Abaseline%3D%2215%22%3E%3C%21--MathML%3A%20%3Cmath%20xmlns%3D%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.w3.org%2F1998%2FMath%2FMathML%22%20style%3D%22font-family%3A%27Times%20New%20Roman%27%22%3E%3Cmsub%3E%3Cmi%3Ep%3C%2Fmi%3E%3Cmi%3Ei%3C%2Fmi%3E%3C%2Fmsub%3E%3C%2Fmath%3E--%3E%3Cdefs%3E%3Cstyle%20type%3D%22text%2Fcss%22%2F%3E%3C%2Fdefs%3E%3Ctext%20font-family%3D%22Times%20New%20Roman%22%20font-size%3D%2216%22%20font-style%3D%22italic%22%20text-anchor%3D%22middle%22%20x%3D%224.5%22%20y%3D%2215%22%3Ep%3C%2Ftext%3E%3Ctext%20font-family%3D%22Times%20New%20Roman%22%20font-size%3D%2212%22%20font-style%3D%22italic%22%20text-anchor%3D%22middle%22%20x%3D%2210.5%22%20y%3D%2222%22%3Ei%3C%2Ftext%3E%3C%2Fsvg%3E)。
